Copyright: See the file COPYRIGHTS for various htslib copyright details 
Description: 
    This package provides a wrapper for the htslib and bcftools libraries, 
    which are used for manipulating genomic data in the Variant Call Format (VCF) 
    and Binary Call Format (BCF). The package includes utility functions for 
    reading, writing, and manipulating VCF/BCF files, as well as for performing 
    common operations such as filtering and merging VCF/BCF files.
